# Camera Data Enriched

This directory contains camera files enriched with OSM road corridor data.

Generated by the PostGIS enrichment pipeline in `tools/enrich_osm/`.

## Fields Added

- `p1`, `p2`: Corridor segment endpoints [lat, lon]
- `brg`: Bearing in degrees (0-359)
- `w`: Corridor half-width in meters
- `psl`: Posted speed limit (if available from OSM)
- `maxspeed_raw`: Raw OSM maxspeed tag
- `oneway`: Oneway tag if present
